## Goal
Stand up the on-disk store with the full users/projects/tasks repository layer, the node:http server, a router whose route modules auto-mount by convention plus an auth-verifier injection point, JSON body parsing, centralized error handling, PORT binding, and the npm start script — so every later capability plugs in a new route module without editing core files.

